OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FA protest has been held following the
OL,7,Fsudden closure of a private school in
OL,8,FDurham.
OL,10,FDurham High School will be closed at
OL,11,Fthe end of the current term, leaving
OL,12,Fits 281 pupils to find places
OL,13,Felsewhere.
OL,15,FIn a statement released this week, the
OL,16,Fschool said: "For 142 proud years,
OL,17,FDurham High School has stood solidly
OL,18,Fas a beacon of hope for girls who were
OL,19,Fonce denied the education enjoyed by
OL,20,Ftheir male counterparts.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,F"During this time, countless scores of
OL,7,Fyoung people have been afforded the
OL,8,Fbest of educations, not just in the
OL,9,Flearnings of the texts they were
OL,10,Ftaught but in the determination,
OL,11,Fresilience and aspiration instilled in
OL,12,Fthem to shape a better world."
OL,14,FThe statement added: "Today, we write
OL,15,Fthe last chapter in this incredible
OL,16,Fhistory. It is a terribly sad chapter
OL,17,Fas our owners are closing the school
OL,18,Fat the end of this term.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
