OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FTo the 281 current pupils, we are
OL,7,Fdeeply sorry you will not have the
OL,8,Fchance to reach the end of your
OL,9,Fjourney in this truly special school.
OL,10,FGo with strength and the values you
OL,11,Fembody to make a difference in your
OL,12,Fnext chapter."
OL,14,FOn Friday (3 July), teachers, school
OL,15,Fstaff and pupils held a demonstration
OL,16,Foutside the gates.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FTeacher Liz Gardner, the school's head
OL,7,Fof geography, said: "I'm just gutted
OL,8,Ffor the children, absolutely gutted.
OL,9,FThere have been so many tears over the
OL,10,Flast few days. I was holding it
OL,11,Ftogether until one of the children
OL,12,Fcame up the corridor after the
OL,13,Fannouncement saying 'all my friends
OL,14,Fare going to different places. This is
OL,15,Fthe only place I can be myself. What
OL,16,Fam I going to do?'
OL,18,F"It's just been devastating."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FShe added: "We need people to
OL,7,Funderstand what's happened here. We
OL,8,Fdon't fully understand what's
OL,9,Fhappened. We were taken over by a
OL,10,Fcompany two years ago and promised
OL,11,Finvestment and this is where we are."
OL,13,FGalaxy Global Education (GGE), which
OL,14,Fowns the school, told the Local
OL,15,FDemocracy Reporting Service that
OL,16,Fdiscussions with potential partners
OL,17,Fhad been unable to secure the school's
OL,18,Ffuture and confirmed Durham Education
OL,19,FLimited, which operates the school,
OL,20,Fwould enter administration after the
OL,21,Fend of term.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FOther schools owned by GGE in Wales
OL,7,Fand Worcestershire have also announced
OL,8,Ftheir closure.
OL,10,FThe company said it was "with great
OL,11,Fsadness" that it had reached the
OL,12,Fdecision and apologised for the
OL,13,Fdistress caused to pupils, families
OL,14,Fand staff.
OL,16,FIt said its immediate priority was
OL,17,F"the wellbeing and continued education
OL,18,Fof every pupil" and that it was
OL,19,Fworking with local schools to secure
OL,20,Fplaces from September.
OL,26,@rD@YOUsD@HO]yD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/9
