PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FIn a separate letter, director Yan Gao
OL,7,Fpraised staff for their
OL,8,F"professionalism, compassion and
OL,9,Fdedication" during what was described
OL,10,Fas an "exceptionally difficult period".
OL,12,F"We are profoundly sorry that we have
OL,13,Fnot been able to achieve a different
OL,14,Foutcome," the letter said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@KO]rD@GOUrD@fO]tD@AOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/9
