FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,FDurham County Council issued a
OL,7,Fstatement on Friday in which they said
OL,8,Fthey were setting aside time to
OL,9,Fsupport parents looking to get their
OL,10,Fchildren into alternative schools. The
OL,11,Flocal authority is also signposting
OL,12,Fstaff to employment opportunities.
OL,14,FCouncillor Cathy Hunt, Durham County
OL,15,FCouncil's cabinet member for children
OL,16,Fand young people's services, said: "We
OL,17,Fwere really sorry to hear the news
OL,18,Fabout Durham High School and fully
OL,19,Fappreciate how concerning this must be
OL,20,Ffor children, parents, and staff.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
