PN,39709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1783698492
OL,3,CProtest held after private school
OL,4,Cannounces sudden closure
OL,6,F"Officers within our admissions team
OL,7,Fare setting aside time to support
OL,8,Fparents looking to get their children
OL,9,Finto alternative schools and have
OL,10,Falready responded to multiple
OL,11,Frequests, offering advice on
OL,12,Favailability of places."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/9
